metadata.description:
heds is honored to introduce the first artist featured via our hedSOLO drops: Dabow. heds has been familiar with Dabow for almost a decade now, witnessing legendary releases over the years, across virtually every digital platform. "Wanna Be" represents a progressive sound, pushing the boundaries of electronica, blending influences from across the globe into one cohesive composition. Here's a short quote from the legend himself on the track:

"Do you ever feel like you WANNA BE something?

Well, say it!

Not easy. 
Long way to go.
Maybe you already are what you wanna be-
Who knows?

in the meantime:
SAY YOU WANNA BE WANNA BE WANNA BE WANNA BE!"

- Dabow

Look forward to more hedSOLO drops via the heds community, exclusively on Sound.
